<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_66238_restlogger.RESTLog</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>RESTLog</name><script><![CDATA[var RESTLog = Class.create();
RESTLog.prototype = {
	initialize: function() {
	},

	log : function(method, request) {

		var msgGr = new GlideRecord(Constants.MESSAGE_TABLE);
		msgGr.newRecord();
		msgGr.setValue('url', request.url);
		msgGr.setValue('uri', request.uri);
		msgGr.setValue('method', method);
		var id = msgGr.insert();

		if (id) {
			this._logJSON(Constants.HEADER_TABLE, msgGr, request.headers);
			this._logJSON(Constants.PATH_PARAM_TABLE, msgGr, request.pathParams);
			this._logJSON(Constants.QUERY_PARAM_TABLE, msgGr, request.queryParams);
		}
	},

	_logJSON : function(tableName, msgGr, obj) {

		for (var k in obj) {
			var gr = new GlideRecord(tableName);
			gr.newRecord();
			gr.setValue('name', k);
			if (typeof obj[k] == "object") {
				gr.setValue('value', JSON.stringify(obj[k]));
			} else {
				gr.setValue('value', obj[k]);
			}
			gr.setValue('message', msgGr.getUniqueValue());
			gr.insert();

		}

	},



	type: 'RESTLogger'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>chuck.tomasi</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-04-29 15:15:18</sys_created_on><sys_id>74586fd8db2c1010d5cc61ca0b9619d6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>RESTLog</sys_name><sys_package display_value="REST Logger" source="x_66238_restlogger">8676eb18db2c1010d5cc61ca0b9619af</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="REST Logger">8676eb18db2c1010d5cc61ca0b9619af</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_74586fd8db2c1010d5cc61ca0b9619d6</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>chuck.tomasi</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-04-29 15:34:43</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
